questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;The pattern followed here is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Logic: (First number)&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ (Third number)&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;= (X&amp;nbsp;&amp;divide; 5)&amp;nbsp;= Second number.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(6, 189, 9)&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; (6)&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ (9)&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;= (216 + 729) = 945&amp;nbsp;&amp;divide;&amp;nbsp;5&amp;nbsp;&amp;rArr; 189&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(5, 225, 10)&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; (5)&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ (10)&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;= (125 + 1000) = 1125&amp;nbsp;&amp;divide; 5 = 225&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Similarly,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(7, 171, 8)&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; (7)&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ (8)&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;= (343 + 512) = 855&amp;nbsp;&amp;divide; 5 = 171&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Option 3&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>এখানে অনুসরণ করা ধাঁচটি&nbsp;হল:</p>

<p><strong>যুক্তি: (প্রথম সংখ্যা)<sup>3</sup> + (তৃতীয় সংখ্যা)<sup>3</sup> = (X &divide; 5) = দ্বিতীয় সংখ্যা।</strong></p>

<p>(6, 189, 9)&nbsp;&rarr; (6)<sup>3</sup>&nbsp;+ (9)<sup>3</sup>&nbsp;= (216 + 729) = 945&nbsp;&divide;&nbsp;5&nbsp;&rArr; 189</p>

<p>এবং,</p>

<p>(5, 225, 10)&nbsp;&rarr; (5)<sup>3</sup>&nbsp;+ (10)<sup>3</sup>&nbsp;= (125 + 1000) = 1125&nbsp;&divide; 5 = 225</p>

<p>একইভাবে,</p>

<p>(7, 171, 8)&nbsp;&rarr; (7)<sup>3</sup>&nbsp;+ (8)<sup>3</sup>&nbsp;= (343 + 512) = 855&nbsp;&divide; 5 = 171</p>

<p>সুতরাং, সঠিক উত্তর হল <strong>"বিকল্প 3"</strong>।</p>

questions.statement:
&lt;p&gt;What approximate value should come in place of the question mark ( ? ) in the following equation ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;44.92 - 84.99 &amp;divide;&amp;nbsp;17.01 + 14.92 &amp;times; 11.08 = ?&lt;/p&gt;<br><p>নিম্নলিখিত সমীকরণে প্রশ্নবোধক চিহ্ন (?) এর স্থানে আনুমানিক কত মান আসবে?</p>

<p>44.92 - 84.99 &divide;&nbsp;17.01 + 14.92 &times; 11.08 = ?</p>

questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;Given:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;44.92 - 84.99 &amp;divide;&amp;nbsp;17.01 + 14.92 &amp;times; 11.08 = ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Approximate value:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;45 - 85 &amp;divide;&amp;nbsp;17&amp;nbsp;+ 15&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Calculate the approximate value:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;=&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;45 - &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;85 &amp;divide;&amp;nbsp;17&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ 15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;=&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;45 - 5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;+ &lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;15&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 11&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;=&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;45&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; - 5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;+ 165&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;=&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt; 210&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;- 5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;= 205&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;205&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>প্রদত্ত:</p>

<p>44.92 - 84.99 &divide;&nbsp;17.01 + 14.92 &times; 11.08 = ?</p>

<p>আনুমানিক মান:</p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">45 - 85 &divide; 17 + 15 &times;&nbsp;11</span></p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">আনুমানিক মান গণনা করুন:</span></p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">=&nbsp;45 -&nbsp;<u><span style="font-weight: bolder;">85 &divide;&nbsp;17</span></u>&nbsp;+ 15&nbsp;&times; 11</p>

<p style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">=&nbsp;45 - 5&nbsp;+&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bolder;"><u>15&nbsp;&times; 11</u></span></p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">= </span><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"><u><strong>45</strong></u> - 5</span><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"> <u><strong>+ 165</strong></u></span></p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">=<u><strong> 210</strong></u></span><u><strong><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);"> - 5</span></strong></u></p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">= 205</span></p>

<p><span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">সুতরাং, সঠিক উত্তর হল <strong>"205".</strong></span></p>

